    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "エキシビジョンマッチ終了から二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Two hours after the exhibition match ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9731891491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "到着ーーー！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arrivedーーー!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.066666468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "んーっ、夜風が気持ちいー。なんだか、こっちに\n戻って来るのはすっごく久しぶりな気がするなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm~‚ the night breeze feels so good‚ Somehow‚ coming back\nhere feels like it's been a really long time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にはたまに帰って来てはいましたが\n十人で……と言うと確かにそうかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have come back to Hoshimi City occasionally‚ but\nwith ten people… you're right‚ it might be‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8422093541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "星見市から羽ばたいた……ライバル二グループが……\nBIG４になって戻って来る……激エモ胸熱展開！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Two rival groups that soared from Hoshimi City…\nReturning as BIG4 members… such an emotional and heartwarming development!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2644586656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "エキシビジョンマッチが終わってすぐに電車に\n乗り込んで来ちゃったけど、終電は大丈夫かしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got on the train right after the exhibition match ended‚\nbut I wonder if we'll be okay for the last train…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.166694019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "いいんじゃない？　今日はみんな実家に泊まれば\nもしくはマネージャーにホテルでも取ってもらいましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't it fine? If everyone stays at their parents' house today‚\nor we can have the manager get us a hotel‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1333336115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！　みんなでお泊まり楽しそー！　……ん？\n見て見て、なんかあっちの方にぼーっと光るものが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Staying over together sounds fun! …Hm?\nLook‚ look‚ there's something glowing faintly over there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7000002782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 68.0666669448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "どこどこ？　もしかしてお化けさんが\n私達を歓迎してくれてるのかな？　おかえりーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where‚ where? Maybe a ghost is\nwelcoming us? Saying‚ \"Welcome back\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7854994778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、二人ともやめてくださいまし！\nお、お化けだなんて、変なことを言わないでくださる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ both of you‚ please stop it!\nP-please don't say strange things like g-ghosts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0000002782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんかもしれないよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be Mana-chan~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3316102975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、麻奈様のお化けでしたらお会いしたいですわね……\nどこにお化けさんがいらっしゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ if it's Lady Mana's ghost‚ I would like to meet it…\nWhere is the ghost…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9333336115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……わっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Whoa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.211947965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーっ！　驚かせるのはやめてくださいまし！\n雫！　なんで突然背後から肩を叩いたんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! Please stop scaring me!\nShizuku! Why did you suddenly tap me on the shoulder from behind!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.034522842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 105.9666674535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。私達、ほんの少し前までステージの上で\n戦ってたんだよね。なんだか全然そんな気がしないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ We were just fighting on stage\nuntil a little while ago‚ I somehow don't feel like that at all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6000007868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうよ。どこにいても、BIG4になっても\n私達は私達。この星見市で出会った仲間なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ No matter where we are‚ even if we become BIG4‚\nwe are who we are‚ Because we're friends who met in this Hoshimi City‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2666674535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～エキシビジョンマッチの月スト本当に凄かったな\nあのパフォーマンスを思い出すとまだドキドキするもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh~ Moon Tempest's exhibition match was really amazing‚\nI still get excited when I remember that performance‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1666674535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……サニピが相手だったから\n私達はあのパフォーマンスが出来たんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… I think we were able to give that performance because Sunny Peace was our opponent‚\nthat we were able to give that performance‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666674535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、次は……ううん、もう絶対にサニピは\n負けないよ。月ストにも他のグループにも、絶対に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But next time… no‚ Sunny Peace will definitely\nnot lose‚ Not to Moon Tempest or any other group‚ absolutely‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4000007868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だって、トップの席は一つしかないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because there's only one seat at the top‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7761908863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 161.2389346772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……。私も負けない\nサニピは……さくらは……私のライバル、だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… I won't lose either‚\nSunny Peace… Sakura… is my rival‚ after all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3333341201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ！　琴乃ちゃん、やーっと私のことを\n『ライバル』って言ってくれた！　初めてだよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Kotono-chan‚ you finally\ncalled me your \"rival\"! This is the first time‚ isn't it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.4340303187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかしら……？　さくらのことは、出会った時\nからずっとライバルだと思ってたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really…? About Sakura‚ from when we met‚\nI've always thought of her as my rival‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3000028213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_14_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_06-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！\n何を二人でいい雰囲気になってるんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on!\nWhat are you two doing‚ getting all lovey-dovey!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.5000028213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
